{"id":"lotan","term":"Lotan","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Coverer, one of the sons of Seir, the Horite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:20\">Gen. 36:20</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:29\">29</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:20","Genesis 36:29"]}